{"id": "1248340612428730400", "channel_id": "1247463554802520065", "type": 0, "author_id": "1002938431271358494", "author_name": "1027vliaji", "author_bot": false, "content": "代发，补一下缘结空蝉的鼠鼠永世流环娜。", "timestamp": "2024-06-06T18:19:55.050000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-06-06T18:22:58.378000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1247463554802520065", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "癫狂五3W分，血肉环娜攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1243105047332524043", "1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1248341212952531045", "channel_id": "1247463554802520065", "type": 0, "author_id": "1002938431271358494", "author_name": "1027vliaji", "author_bot": false, "content": "开局的钥令是【鼠鼠智慧】或者【血与沙】。【血与沙】的道中会轻松一些，但是需要算力造物补充BOSS战的算力。然后环娜选择带【巨人之刃】，减费用，不然算力不够叠力量。", "timestamp": "2024-06-06T18:22:18.226000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-06-06T18:26:48.198000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1247463554802520065", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "癫狂五3W分，血肉环娜攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1243105047332524043", "1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1248341246079012926", "channel_id": "1247463554802520065", "type": 0, "author_id": "1002938431271358494", "author_name": "1027vliaji", "author_bot": false, "content": "5回合之前基本都是鼠鼠智慧，然后羊妈【古老爱抚】留在每回合最后3张，下回合环娜再大招拿回来，羊妈再复制。爆掉死抗之后选【永世执念】打爆发。", "timestamp": "2024-06-06T18:22:26.124000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-06-06T18:27:00.167000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1247463554802520065", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "癫狂五3W分，血肉环娜攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1243105047332524043", "1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1248342130028707910", "channel_id": "1247463554802520065", "type": 0, "author_id": "1002938431271358494", "author_name": "1027vliaji", "author_bot": false, "content": "另外补充一下，如果拿了臭脚，然后没有镜像和【意识铭刻】留命定的情况下。就在本回合环娜开大选择钥令【跨越洄溯之扉】，然后下回合开钥令抓取【命定之剑】。环娜不开大，羊妈复制就行。不过这个打法只能给【藏品】环娜用，【巨人之刃】的环娜还是不拿臭脚比较好。", "timestamp": "2024-06-06T18:25:56.874000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-06-06T18:26:05.154000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1247463554802520065", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "癫狂五3W分，血肉环娜攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1243105047332524043", "1174179734373019748"]}
